    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear 8,000 RPM power band. This specimen has been maintained with technical foresight; the VANOS unit has been overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M-differential for precise power delivery out of corners. While the car shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver's machine, the suspension geometry remains true and the engine pull is vigorous. It is a turn-key example for the enthusiast who prioritizes visceral performance and mechanical integrity over trailer-queen status.",
      "price": 34500.0,
