    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for premium sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Charcoal Grey Metallic that still retains a high-gloss luster; upon close inspection, you will find only minor surface scratches and small rock chips on the hood consistent with careful road use. The interior features a smoke-free, black leather environment. The upholstery is supple and free of tears, though there is some light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the updated touchscreen navigation system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles, with the most recent maintenance including a fresh synthetic oil change and a new cabin air filter.",
      "price": 35000.0,
